channel.title: Helping people with JAVA problems only
channel.description:
Seeing how everyone is making help threads now, I decided to make one now. This is only for problems with CODING JAVA, if you ask me anything about "How do I start my server" or "Whats this javac error" I will ignore you completely.
Fire away.
